    "description": "<strong>Can you get the ball to the end?</strong> It's a simple question. Rage Ball is a physics-driven platformer. Master the physics to reach the end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/1b1c51e9eff57e0dd7e454fd028e6a67.poster.avif?t=1768777593\" width=300 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/1b1c51e9eff57e0dd7e454fd028e6a67.webm?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/1b1c51e9eff57e0dd7e454fd028e6a67.mp4?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/0d07ad8a747eee4e7e54a8cc1434b83e.poster.avif?t=1768777593\" width=300 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/0d07ad8a747eee4e7e54a8cc1434b83e.webm?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/0d07ad8a747eee4e7e54a8cc1434b83e.mp4?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Ultra realistic ball physics</u></strong> with full momentum and friction dynamics.<br></li><li><strong><u>State of the art graphics</u></strong> with realistic water, reflections, and Global Illumination.<br></li><li><strong><u>Checkpoints</u></strong> will save your progress should you fall.<br></li><li><strong><u>Stat tracking</u></strong> for infinite replayability and speedrunning attempts.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/f216245e436ec955145ce071ef6a4c05.poster.avif?t=1768777593\" width=300 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/f216245e436ec955145ce071ef6a4c05.webm?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/f216245e436ec955145ce071ef6a4c05.mp4?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/213445c12a060a7a1b269def7fb907b2.poster.avif?t=1768777593\" width=300 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/213445c12a060a7a1b269def7fb907b2.webm?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/213445c12a060a7a1b269def7fb907b2.mp4?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rage Ball is a physics-based test of skill and patience. Your task is to guide the ball to the end without falling. However, if you do fall, you may return to the previous checkpoint.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/ed309f427e59625efc3a059123bfa6b9.poster.avif?t=1768777593\" width=300 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/ed309f427e59625efc3a059123bfa6b9.webm?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173270/extras/ed309f427e59625efc3a059123bfa6b9.mp4?t=1768777593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted lo